        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0057-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:49:29.634+09:00">The Dao begets the One;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:49:33.73+09:00">the One begets two;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:49:50.784+09:00">two beget three;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:50:23.797+09:00">and three beget the myriad things.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:56:22.567+09:00">The Dao that can be described in language</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:56:29.026+09:00">is not the constantDao;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:56:40.501+09:00">the name that can be given it</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:56:48.9+09:00">is not its constant name.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:57:14.703+09:00">Nameless, it is the origin of the myriad things;*</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:57:47.672+09:00">named, it is themother of the myriad things.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:58:14.157+09:00">Therefore, always be without desire so as to see their subtlety.‘</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:58:43.628+09:00">And always have desire so as to see their ends.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:59:01.199+09:00">These two emerge together but have different names.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:59:07.55+09:00">Together,we refer to them as mystery:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T16:59:15.126+09:00">the mystery upon mystery</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T17:00:04.845+09:00">and gatewayof all subtleties.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
